snippet.textDisplay:
I don’t have one but I’ve been eyeing glass pens for a while. I’m not an artist though. My interest is because I love glassblowing and have done some, so the it’s pretty. I’m also a writer and while not something I would use for routine writing I think it would make a gorgeous and swank pen for signing books.
I would probably compare it to other dip pens than to your regular art pens. It does seem like it would be more suited to a different art style than what you typically do and that your side by side comparison is maybe not the fairest comparison but it did well in spite of that.
